"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"FAUNA:5.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.2</span> 标题：青蛙（frog）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צְפַרְדֵּעַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsefarde‘a)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:27\">EXO 7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:28\">EXO 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:29\">EXO 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:1\">EXO 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:2\">EXO 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:3\">EXO 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:4\">EXO 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:5\">EXO 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:7\">EXO 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:8\">EXO 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:9\">EXO 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:45\">PSA 78:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:30\">PSA 105:30</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：βάτραχος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：batrachos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:13\">REV 16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis19:10\">WIS 19:10</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">讨论</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0247_frog.jpg\" alt=\"青蛙\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">青蛙 (Pixabay)</figcaption></figure>这两个希伯来文和希腊文词语的意思是&quot;青蛙&quot;，对此基本上没有学者提出质疑。《出埃及记》中提到的青蛙之灾发生在河水被污染（变成血）的灾害之后。可以推断，青蛙因此从水里上来，进入了各个村庄。由于青蛙捕食苍蝇，可以控制苍蝇数量，所以，青蛙的大量死亡很可能导致埃及遭受另外两个灾祸，即蚊灾和蝇灾。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0248_frogs.jpg\" alt=\"青蛙\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">青蛙 (Pixabay)</figcaption></figure>在中东和埃及，最常见的两种青蛙是肉蛙（学名<em>Rana esculenta</em> ）和斑点蛙（学名<em>Rana punctata</em> ）。这两种青蛙的身长大约7厘米（3英寸），体色为棕色或橄榄绿色。青蛙几乎一直栖息在水中，以蚊蚋、苍蝇和其他水边的昆虫为食。青蛙为卵生，卵先孵化成蝌蚪，然后逐渐长出四条腿。后腿比前腿粗大得多，也有力得多，因为青蛙是用后腿跳跃的。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">特殊意义或象征意义</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>犹太人认为青蛙在礼仪上不洁净。埃及人和波斯人也这样认为，因为他们将青蛙与鬼魔联系在一起。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>世界各地都有青蛙，因此找到当地的对等词来翻译&quot;青蛙&quot;应该没有困难。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
